Achievements.Name: The start
Achievements.Description: You've finished the first chapter! Of course, that was just a warm-up!

Achievements.Name: So, what is it?
Achievements.Description: You've found the first testimony in a long series.

Achievements.Name: The best Subject
Achievements.Description: It's been a long time since a Subject tried to cheat. You're the best.

Achievements.Name: I'm a liar
Achievements.Description: You chose to lie. It isn't good to lie, you know.

Achievements.Name: Desperate Subject
Achievements.Description: You chose to talk to the entity and tell it everything. What a gossip!

Achievements.Name: Incorruptible Subject
Achievements.Description: You chose difficulty and grey matter. You are now rewarded!

Achievements.Name: Cold-blooded Subject
Achievements.Description: You managed to master your mind and beauty. It's wonderful.

Achievements.Name: Did you say monkey business?
Achievements.Description: You solved the 3 monkeys' enigma. You're a genius!

Achievements.Name: Some fresh air?
Achievements.Description: You've finished the second chapter. Did you need some fresh air, Subject 13?

Achievements.Name: Are you lost?
Achievements.Description: Better than the company of a ball, you've beaten the jungle with your mind!

Achievements.Name: Revelation?
Achievements.Description: Subject 13? Have you gone? Clearly, you've left our land...

Achievements.Name: Informed Subject
Achievements.Description: You've found half of the testimonies. You still have work to do, Subject 13!

Achievements.Name: You know everything
Achievements.Description: You know everything... Terrifying isn't it?
